    <stitle>CE 200, CE 300 - HOOD, GRILLE, FENDERS AND BUMPER - Description - Hood Stop Assembly</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Hood Stop Assembly</title>
        <para>The hood stop assembly (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0900922">Figure 22</hotlnk>) is mounted each side of the cowl. The hood stop allows the
            hood to rest at a certain designed height to allow clearance for the components under the hood. The hood
            stop bushing is also designed to aid in the ease of operation in tilting the hood.
        </para>
